<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password for Tradeboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .otp {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Reset Your Tradeboard Password</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>You have requested to reset your password for Tradeboard. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to
            complete the password reset process:</p>
        <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 10 minutes. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email and
            ensure your account is secure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>